<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.5.1">
<l>eṅṅaṉēyō vaṉṉai mīrkā ḷeṉṉai muṉivatunīr</l>
<l>naṅkaḷkō lattiruk kuṟuṅkuṭi nampiyai nāṉkaṇṭapiṉ</l>
<l>caṅkiṉōṭu nēmi yōṭun tāmaraik kaṇkaḷoṭuñ</l>
<l>ceṅkaṉivā yoṉṟi ṉōṭuñ celkiṉṟa teṉṉeñcamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>How [is it], mothers, [that] you disapprove of me?</l>
<l>After I saw our Nampi of beautiful Tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi,</l>
<l>my heart goes for the conch and the discus</l>
<l>and the lotus eyes and the one mouth [like] a red ripe fruit.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
